caption: A man with short dark hair, wearing a light blue patterned shirt and a dark tie with white patterns, stands in front of a cityscape backdrop during sunset, holding a tablet and appearing to present news.

A man wearing a blue shirt and a face mask is handling a large cardboard box near a forklift in what appears to be a warehouse or loading area.

A man wearing a bright yellow safety vest and a yellow hard hat walks along a paved sidewalk, carrying a yellow helmet in his arms, while another worker in similar attire walks beside him. The scene is set outdoors in an urban area with trees and storefronts visible in the background.
A young boy in a light blue school uniform shirt and dark tie speaks to the camera outdoors, with a school building and dirt ground visible in the background.

A street scene featuring a group of women protesting, many wearing purple shirts and holding red cards aloft, with one woman in the foreground holding a sign that reads "SO NUEVA!!" and another wearing a shirt with the text "Movimiento por Dignidad de las..." and a question mark symbol.

A news anchor in a studio setting, wearing a white blouse and dark pants, sits behind a modern desk with a red and white logo, holding a red object, against a backdrop of a city skyline at sunset. A wide, empty airport tarmac under an overcast sky, with distant mountains on the horizon and a few birds in flight; white runway markings are visible in the foreground.

The posters are taped to a surface, with one in dark background and the other in light green, and a QR code is visible on the left poster. A street scene in a commercial district with multi-story buildings featuring Asian-inspired architecture, including wooden balconies and vertical signage; a red neon sign reading "HOUSE HOT" is visible on the right, and a pedestrian bridge with red umbrellas spans across the street in the midground.

A woman with long, dark braided hair adorned with a red ribbon stands on a platform, wearing a vibrant pink skirt and a patterned top, facing a large crowd at an outdoor event under a clear blue sky.

A man in a green patterned shirt and dark shorts walks through a brightly lit shopping mall corridor, carrying a brown paper bag, while other shoppers, including a woman in a white tank top and beige pants, move nearby past a ZARA store display.

A bustling supermarket checkout area at a WinMart store, with customers in casual attire—some wearing patterned shirts and hats—waiting in line, while staff in red uniforms assist at registers under bright fluorescent lighting and prominent red signage.

An aerial view of an industrial complex featuring multiple red-and-white striped smokestacks, large cylindrical tanks, and interconnected buildings, surrounded by green fields and roads, with a river visible in the background.

A street scene at night featuring a white pickup truck with its headlights on, approaching a checkpoint where two individuals stand near the roadside—one wearing a high-visibility yellow vest and the other in dark clothing. A blurry on-site scene from a news report, showing a person in a white shirt and dark pants moving quickly through what appears to be a cluttered indoor space with stacked items and dim lighting. The image is shaky, suggesting motion capture during an incident.

A man in a green shirt is seated at a table, writing on paper, while another man in a dark gray shirt gestures beside him. A uniformed officer sits across from them, and a standing officer in a beige uniform observes. Behind them, a large monitor displays multiple security camera feeds, and metal filing cabinets line the wall.

A group of men in uniform and casual attire sit around a polished table, signing documents; one man in a tan uniform holds a black bag while others write with pens, with a monitor displaying surveillance footage in the background.

A tiger with distinct black and white stripes is walking across a sandy or gravelly ground, carrying several small tiger cubs in its mouth. The scene is captured in black and white, with a brick wall in the background and timestamp and news channel logos visible on the screen.

A woman with short, gray hair, wearing a white jacket, a black top, and a prominent turquoise necklace with large beads, smiles while speaking into a microphone during an on-site interview. Two women in a brightly lit indoor setting, each holding a cat, are featured in a news segment. A man with dark, curly hair and a mustache, wearing a teal zip-up jacket, stands outdoors at night, speaking to the camera. Behind him, strings of warm lights illuminate rows of plants or crops, suggesting a farm or garden setting.

A conceptual architectural rendering of a futuristic urban development project, featuring a central circular water body surrounded by high-rise buildings, green spaces, and labeled zones such as "International Hotel," "The Gateway," and "Aquarium," with a river flowing alongside the complex.

A street scene featuring a line of uniformed soldiers in dark formal attire with white stripes down their trousers and tall black hats, standing at attention, while civilians in olive-green jackets and trousers observe or walk past.
